properties.areaDesc: Coastal Waters from Schoodic Point, ME to Stonington, ME out 25 NM
properties.headline: Small Craft Advisory issued January 26 at 6:42AM EST until January 27 at 4:00AM EST by NWS Caribou ME
properties.description:
* WHAT...Southwest winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and
seas 7 to 12 feet.

* WHERE...Coastal Waters from Schoodic Point, ME to Stonington,
ME out 25 NM.

* WHEN...Until 4 AM EST Monday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.
properties.instruction:
Inexperienced mariners, especially those operating smaller
vessels, should avoid navigating in hazardous conditions.

NWSheadline: SMALL CRAFT ADVISORY IN EFFECT UNTIL 4 AM EST MONDAY... ...GALE WARNING IS CANCELLED
